TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed AutoCompleteType extends System.Enum

summary.span: 表示可以控制 控制項中 [自動完成] 功能行為的值。

span.span: Represents the values that control the behavior of the AutoComplete feature in a control.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 為了協助資料輸入，Internet Explorer 5 和更新版本以及某些其他瀏覽器支援名為 「 自動完成 」 的功能。To assist with data entry, Internet Explorer 5 and later and some other browsers support a feature named AutoComplete. 自動完成會監視文字方塊中，並會儲存一份使用者所輸入的值。AutoComplete monitors a text box and stores a list of the values that the user has entered. 當使用者返回文字另一次，會顯示值的清單。When the user returns to the text box another time, the list of values is displayed. 而不是重新輸入值，使用者可以直接從這份清單選取值。Instead of retyping a value, the user can simply select the value from this list. > [!NOTE] > 並非所有的瀏覽器支援的自動完成功能。Not all browsers support the AutoComplete feature. 請洽詢您的瀏覽器，來判斷相容性。Check with your browser to determine compatibility. 若要控制的自動完成功能的行為控制項，您使用屬性。To control the behavior of the AutoComplete feature for a control, you use the property. 列舉型別用來表示的值，您可以套用至屬性。The enumeration is used to represent the values that you can apply to the property. 根據預設，屬性控制設為 `AutoCompleteType.None`。By default, the property for a control is set to `AutoCompleteType.None`. 使用此設定時，控制項與其他共用清單控制具有相同跨不同的頁面。With this setting, the control shares the list with other controls with the same across different pages. 您也可以共用的清單之間而不是類別，依據控制項根據。You can also share a list among controls based on a category instead of based on an . 當您設定其中一個類別目錄值的屬性 (例如`AutoCompleteType.FirstName`或`AutoCompleteType.LastName`)，則所有控制項相同的類別目錄和共用相同的清單。When you set the property to one of the category values (such as `AutoCompleteType.FirstName` or `AutoCompleteType.LastName`), all controls with the same category share the same list. 您可以停用自動完成功能，如控制項，藉由設定屬性設`AutoCompleteType.Disabled`。You can disable the AutoComplete feature for a control by setting the property to `AutoCompleteType.Disabled`. 請參閱您的瀏覽器文件，如需有關設定並啟用自動完成功能。Refer to your browser documentation for details on configuring and enabling the AutoComplete feature. 例如，若要啟用自動完成功能，在 Internet Explorer 第 5 版或更新版本中，從**工具**功能表上，選擇**網際網路選項**。For example, to enable the AutoComplete feature in Internet Explorer version 5 or later, from the **Tools** menu, choose **Internet Options**. 然後選擇**內容** 索引標籤。選擇**自動完成**來檢視和修改的自動完成功能的選項按鈕。Then choose the **Content** tab. Choose the **AutoComplete** button to view and modify options for the AutoComplete feature. 如需有關在 Internet Explorer 中的自動完成功能的詳細資訊，搜尋[使用 HTML 表單的 AutoComplete](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/workshop/author/forms/autocomplete_ovr.asp)位於 MSDN Library， http://msdn.microsoft.com/library。For more information on the AutoComplete feature in Internet Explorer, search for [Using AutoComplete in HTML Forms](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/workshop/author/forms/autocomplete_ovr.asp) in the MSDN Library at http://msdn.microsoft.com/library. ## Examples 下列範例示範如何使用列舉型別到指定的自動完成類別控制項。The following example demonstrates how to use the enumeration to specify the AutoComplete category for a control. > [!IMPORTANT] > 這個範例有一個可接受使用者輸入的文字方塊，這可能會造成安全性威脅。This example has a text box that accepts user input, which is a potential security threat. 根據預設，ASP.NET Web 網頁會驗證使用者輸入未包含指令碼或 HTML 項目。By default, ASP.NET Web pages validate that user input does not include script or HTML elements. 如需詳細資訊，請參閱 [Script Exploits Overview](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/772c7312-211a-4eb3-8d6e-eec0aa1dcc07) (指令碼攻擊概觀)。For more information, see [Script Exploits Overview](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/772c7312-211a-4eb3-8d6e-eec0aa1dcc07).
